name: Vita Celestine
description:
A request of @DCl.

Vita Celestine is a Twitch streamer and social media celebrity.

I gotta admit this was probably the toughest TI I've worked on so far. The pictures I got from her Instagram account lacked the quality I'm used to, and my final dataset was probably not good enough to create a decent embedding. After several failed attempts, I checked step #100 of my final try and... well, I'm not sure. The accuracy could be improved, but it does look good on most of the prompts I've tested, though, so I've decided to upload it. Hope you'll like it!

If you get saturated results, remember that you can reduce the embedding's weight in your prompt! Try something like "(vit4100:0.98)", see if the pics look better.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee!
